      "text": "Un Josawats darrija\nMeeru ar to Israëta Kehnixu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kas wehl no Josawata\nLeetahm atleck / un winna\nSpehks/ ko wiꞥſch irr parabdijs/\nun ka wiꞥſch irr karrojs / tas\nwifs irr rakstihts to Kehnixu no\nJuhda Laiku-Grahinata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 47,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch arri tsdsinne no\ntahs Semmes tobß atlikkuschus\nManzincekus/ kas Affus winna\nTehwa Laikā bij atlikkuscht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 48,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "To brihdi ne weens Keh-\nninsch bija Gedoma / bet weens\nKehnixu Pawaldneeks /\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 49,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Josawats likke Juh-\nras Laiwas darriht/ kam bij us\nOwiru pehz Selta eet. Bet tahs\nne gabje / jo tahs Laiwas tappe\nEzeon-Geberā tadansitas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 50,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Akasijus Aka-\nba Dehlsus Josawatu: Lai man-\nnt Kalpt ar taweem Kalpeem lib-\ndst eet us Laiwahn. Bet Josa-\nwats ne gribbeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 51,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Josawats aismitge\nar taweem Tehweem / un tapve\npee taweem Tehweem Dahwida\nPilli aprakts. Un winna Dehts\nJorams tappe par Kehnixu win-\nna Weeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 52,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N Akasijus Akaba\nDehls / tappe pa\nKehnixu pahr J\nsraëlu eekſch Sa\nmartijas/septitā pa\ndefunitā Gaddā Josawata te\nKehntxa no Juhda/ un waldije\ndivi Gaddus pahr Israëlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 53,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrija / ka\ntam KUNGAM ne patikke / u\nstaigaja wiſſs Zeltos fatw\nTehwa un Jawas Mahtes / u\nus Jerobeama Neebata Dehls\nZeltiem / kas Israëlu darrij\ngrehkoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 54,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch kalpoja Ba-\nlain/ un klannijahs preekſch ta\nun apkaitinaja to KUNGU Isra-\netā Deewu/ pehz wiſſu/ ko win-\nna Tehws bij darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Moabs atkahpe no\nsraëta/ kad Akabs bija nomirrie\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Akasijus kritte zau\nSkadrineem jawā augstā Isra-\nbā/ kas eekſch Samarijas bija\nun tappe neuweffels / un win-\nfuhtija Wehsnefchus/ un fazzij\nus teem: Eita / un waizaje\nBaal-Seebubu to Deewu\nEkrona/ arrig es no schahs M\nweffelbas atspirgschohs ?\n"
    }
  ],
